    <item>
      <title>预算之争导致法国债券风险达到欧元危机以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/french-bond-risk-hits-highest-since-euro-crisis-on-budget-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于法国预算引发的政治僵局可能导致法国政府垮台，衡量法国债券风险的指标升至欧元区债务危机以来的最高收盘点位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/french-bond-risk-hits-highest-since-euro-crisis-on-budget-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 17:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大石油行业警告特朗普的关税将提高美国汽油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/canada-s-oil-patch-warns-trump-s-tariffs-would-raise-us-gasoline-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大石油行业强调其对美国出口的经济和安全效益，同时利用候任总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对该国商品征收关税的机会批评总理贾斯汀·特鲁多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/canada-s-oil-patch-warns-trump-s-tariffs-would-raise-us-gasoline-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大股市因特朗普关税威胁而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/canadian-stocks-drop-as-traders-sell-into-trump-s-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周一晚间威胁对加拿大和墨西哥生产的商品征收 25% 的关税，随后工业股周二领跌多伦多股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/canadian-stocks-drop-as-traders-sell-into-trump-s-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:47:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税威胁减弱利好效应 美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/treasuries-slip-as-trump-s-tariff-threats-dim-the-bessent-effect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对美国贸易伙伴征收额外关税之后，美国国债价格下跌，部分抹去了选择斯科特·贝森特出任国防部长所带来的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/treasuries-slip-as-trump-s-tariff-threats-dim-the-bessent-effect</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:47:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫斯基中游考虑本周发售加元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/husky-midstream-weighs-canadian-dollar-bond-sale-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，管道公司 Husky Midstream LP 考虑最早于本周发行至少 4 亿加元（2.84 亿美元）的加元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/husky-midstream-weighs-canadian-dollar-bond-sale-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受可可价格上涨影响的巧克力制造商仍需重建对冲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/chocolate-companies-burned-by-cocoa-price-rally-still-need-to-rebuild-hedges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球巧克力制造商都在观望巧克力价格会跌到什么程度，然后再采取下一步行动，他们意识到自己可能已经错过了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/chocolate-companies-burned-by-cocoa-price-rally-still-need-to-rebuild-hedges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安哥拉称不会就可能的新 IMF 贷款计划进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/angola-says-no-negotiations-on-possible-new-imf-loan-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉表示，目前尚未与国际货币基金组织就可能的新金融援助计划进行谈判。该国的欧元债券暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/angola-says-no-negotiations-on-possible-new-imf-loan-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 12:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金早盘因特朗普关税威胁而下跌，目前持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普威胁对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的进口关税，美元上涨，金价早盘下跌，之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 00:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
